  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the oven to 400°F (200°C).",
    "Roast the red peppers in the oven for 30 minutes, or until the skin is charred and blistered.",
    "Remove the peppers from the oven and let them cool. Peel off the skin, discarding it, and slice them into strips.",
    "In a small bowl, whisk together the shio-koji cure, garlic, oregano, and red pepper flakes.",
    "Place the reblochon cheese on the tagliere and top it with the shio-koji cure mixture.",
    "Arrange the artichoke hearts, roasted red peppers, and red onion slices on top of the cheese.",
    "Drizzle the lemon juice and olive oil over the top, then sprinkle with parsley.",
    "Serve immediately, garnished with additional parsley if desired."
  ],
